    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ABOUT THIS GAME</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cult: MANOS</i> is a loving homage to the Z-class cult movies that are so bad, they become art. We took the legendary <i>Manos: The Hands of Fate</i> and did the only logical thing: remade it as a game where every infamous flaw is now a feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For decades, we laughed at the silence. The glitches. The bizarre acting. We thought they were mistakes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We were wrong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cult: MANOS</i> is a psychological survival horror game hidden beneath a comedy. Peel back the camp and discover what Margaret was really experiencing—and why she needed you to laugh.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Led by industry veterans, this is a handcrafted passion project designed to get under your skin. It honors the source material's bizarre charm, then peels it back to show you why comedy is the ultimate defense mechanism.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The survivors are waiting for you to discover the true meaning of Manos: the god of primal darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>&quot;I look forward to seeing it.&quot;</u></strong><u> — <i>Jackey Raye Neyman Jones, the original Debbie (1966)</i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/1428c37b1b2bbfc58c74ac08ce680f19.poster.avif?t=1768764465\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/1428c37b1b2bbfc58c74ac08ce680f19.webm?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/1428c37b1b2bbfc58c74ac08ce680f19.mp4?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/d95195031bf7178e2f70e4dd436a589d.poster.avif?t=1768764465\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/d95195031bf7178e2f70e4dd436a589d.webm?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Film Reimagined:</strong> Relive the plot of the cult classic <i>Manos: The Hands of Fate</i> in a 2D puzzle-adventure format that explores the story's hidden psychological depths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flaws as Features:</strong> Experience a unique gameplay loop where the original movie's technical failures—out-of-focus shots, awkward acting, and poor sound—are your core mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/f8bc0f2ba1fa9e7f4ba2ddcc2e69b1d0.poster.avif?t=1768764465\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/f8bc0f2ba1fa9e7f4ba2ddcc2e69b1d0.webm?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/f8bc0f2ba1fa9e7f4ba2ddcc2e69b1d0.mp4?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted Analog Horror:</strong> Uncover a hidden narrative of trauma and abuse, presented through a distorted and unsettling VHS aesthetic. Every visual and sound is meticulously designed to evoke the feeling of a lost, cursed videotape—no AI shortcuts, just pure analog dread.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/013bc1ce2a4d021ff385267832fc8d70.poster.avif?t=1768764465\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/013bc1ce2a4d021ff385267832fc8d70.webm?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277770/extras/013bc1ce2a4d021ff385267832fc8d70.mp4?t=1768764465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
